Download Followings: (Note: Please be careful the versions)

  Java 8 
      http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html
      
  Python 3.5.3
      https://www.python.org/downloads/
      
  Hadoop 2.6.5
    http://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.cgi/hadoop/common/hadoop-2.6.5/hadoop-2.6.5.tar.gz
    
  Spark 2.0.2 (Prebuild for Hadoop 2.6)
    http://spark.apache.org/downloads.html
    
  WinUtils (put winutils.exe in the %HADOOP_HOME%\bin)
    https://github.com/srccodes/hadoop-common-2.2.0-bin/archive/master.zip

set environment variables
  JAVA_HOME=D:\Java\jdk1.8.0_111\jre
  SPARK_HOME=D:\Spark
  PYTHONPATH=%SPARK_HOME%\python\lib\pyspark.zip;%SPARK_HOME%\python\lib\py4j-0.10.3-src.zip
  HADOOP_HOME=D:\Hadoop
  
Run spark-shell from %SPARK_HOME%/bin

That is it! Easy!
